<h2 class="blog-h2">Why Automate Your Blog?</h2>
<h3 class="blog-h3">The Power of No-Code Publishing</h3>
<p class="blog-p">In this guide, we’ll walk through building a fully automated blog post pipeline using n8n and GitHub. No backend, no database, just pure automation.</p>
<p class="blog-p"><strong>n8n + GitHub</strong> is the ultimate combo for indie bloggers.</p>
